cc:Work.dc:title: Continuous radon monitor
cc:Work.dc:description:
Continuous radon monitor
Clipart was inspired by the portable radon monitor "Radim 3A" designed by Jiri Plch from the Czech Republic. The device uses silicon-semiconductor alpha-detector.
